#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Kei a Grylli ngā tohutohu ā-roto i roto i te taupānga hei āwhina i a koe ki "
"te whirihora me te whakahaere i tō whakatutukitanga."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Ka hoatu tēnei whārangi i te whānui o ngā āhuatanga matua me ngā hononga "
"tika e taea ai e rātou te whakahaere."

