#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:169
msgid "Download My Data"
msgstr "Tikiake ahau i ōku Raraunga"

#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:171
msgid ""
"Download all your account data as a JSON file. This includes your reminders,"
" messages, email settings, and more. The file is for your records only and "
"cannot be imported back. Protect it as it may contain sensitive information."
msgstr ""
"Tikiake ō pūkete raraunga katoa hei kōnae JSON. Kei roto ko ō whakamahara, "
"karere, tautuhinga īmēra, me ētahi atu atu. Māu anake te pūkete, kāore e "
"taea te whakahoki mai. Tiakina i te mea ka taea te whai mōhiotanga tairongo."

#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:175
msgid "Download My Data (JSON)"
msgstr "Tikiake ahau i ōku Raraunga (JSON)"

#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:179
msgid "Danger Zone"
msgstr "Rōpū Wā mōrearea"

#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:180
msgid "Deleting your account is permanent and cannot be undone."
msgstr "Ko te muku i tō pūkete he pumau, ā, kāore e taea te whakahoki."

#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:185
msgid "Delete My Account"
msgstr "Whakahou Pūkete"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:8
msgid "Translations - Grylli"
msgstr "Whakamaoritanga - Grylli"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:17
#: app/templates/partials/header.html:102
msgid "Translations"
msgstr "Whakamāoritanga"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:20
msgid "Grylli currently supports multiple languages and more will be added."
msgstr ""
"I tēnei wā kei te tautoko a Grylli i ngā reo maha, ā, he maha atu ka "
"tāpirihia."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:21
msgid "Many of the translations were performed with assistance from ChatGPT."
msgstr "He maha o ngā whakamāoritanga i mahia āwhina e ChatGPT."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:22
msgid ""
"If you find a translation issue or want to suggest improvements, your input "
"is welcome!"
msgstr ""
"Mēnā ka kite koe i tētahi take whakamāori, he hiahia rānei ki te tuku "
"whakaaro, ka manakohia ō whakaaro!"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:28
msgid "How to request translation updates"
msgstr "Me pēhea te tono whakahou whakamāoritanga"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:30
msgid "To contribute to translations, please use the following guidelines:"
msgstr ""
"Hei tāpae ki ngā whakamāoritanga, ā, whakamahia ngā aratohu e whai ake nei:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:43
msgid "Contribute missing or improved translations:"
msgstr "Kua kitea he whakamāoritanga ngaro?"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:63
msgid "Open the relevant .po translation file for your language."
msgstr "Tuwhera i te kōnae JSON whakamāori mō tō reo. Hei tauira:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:67
msgid ""
"Find untranslated or incomplete entries and add or improve translations."
msgstr ""
"Kimihia ngā urunga kāore anō kia whakamāoritia, kāore rānei i oti, ka "
"tāpirihia, whakapaihia rānei ngā whakamāoritanga."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:68
msgid "You may use a PO file editor or a text editor."
msgstr ""
"Ka taea e koe te whakamahi i tētahi kaitakatuka kōnae PO, i tētahi "
"kaitakatuka kuputuhi rānei."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:69
msgid "Copy the file path and the snippet of your changes."
msgstr "Tāruatia te ara kōnae me te putakipū o ngā huringa i mahia e koe."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:70
msgid "Paste the snippet directly into a new GitHub issue for review."
msgstr "Whakapirihia te wāwāhi i tāruatia ki te kōrero take GitHub."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:72
msgid "Please do not upload the full .po file to avoid merge conflicts."
msgstr "Kaua e tukuatu i te kōnae .po katoa kia karo i ngā huringa tātārongo."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:85
msgid "Improving existing translations:"
msgstr "Te whakapai ake i ngā whakamāoritanga kē:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:104
msgid "Open the relevant .po file for the translation you want to improve."
msgstr ""
"Tuwhera i te kōnae .po e hāngai ana mō te whakamāoritanga e hiahia ana koe "
"ki te pai ake."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:106
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "Hei tauira:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:110
msgid ""
"Find the phrase(s) and its existing translation(s) you want to improve."
msgstr ""
"Kimihia te/nga rerenga kōrero me tāna/āna whakamāoritanga e hiahia ana koe "
"ki te pai ake."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:111
msgid "Update the phrase(s)."
msgstr "Whakahouhia te/nga rerenga kōrero."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:112
msgid "Copy the file name and path into the issue."
msgstr "Tāruatia te ingoa kōnae me te ara ki te take."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:114
msgid "Paste the copied snippet directly into the GitHub issue comment."
msgstr "Whakapirihia te wāwāhi i tāruatia ki te kōrero take GitHub."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:115
msgid "Do not upload the full .po file to avoid merge conflicts."
msgstr "Kaua e tukuatu i te kōnae .po katoa kia karo i ngā huringa tātārongo."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:118
msgid "Example snippet:"
msgstr "Hei tauira wāwāhi:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:137
msgid "Report missing translations not yet discovered:"
msgstr "Ripoatahia ngā whakamāoritanga ngaro kāore anō kia kitea:"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:154
msgid ""
"If you see text in the app that appears untranslated or missing, please "
"report it to us."
msgstr ""
"Ki te kite koe i ngā kuputaka i te taupānga e āhua kāhore anō kia "
"whakamāoritia, kia ngaro rānei, tēnā tukuna mai te ripoata ki a mātou."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:155
msgid "Provide the exact English phrase as it appears on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Whakahokia mai te rerenga kōrero Pākehā tino rite ki te kitea i runga i te "
"mata."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:156
msgid ""
"Include the page or section where you saw the phrase (e.g., Apprise page, "
"Account Page, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Whakauruhia te whārangi, wāhanga rānei i kite koe i te rerenga kōrero (hei "
"tauira, Whārangi Whakaturanga, Wāhanga Pūkete)."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:157
msgid ""
"Submit this information via a new GitHub issue so we can add it to the "
"translation files"
msgstr ""
"Tukua tēnei mōhiohio mā tētahi take GitHub hou kia tāpiri e mātou ki ngā "
"kōnae whakamāoritanga ka takai hoki mō Babel."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:166
msgid "Found a missing translation?"
msgstr "Kua kitea he whakamāoritanga ngaro?"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:171
msgid ""
"This link will create a new GitHub issue pre-filled with a language code."
msgstr ""
"Ka waihangatia e tēnei hono he take GitHub hōu kua whakaōtaua ki tētahi "
"waehere reo."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:172
msgid "Report it by opening a new GitHub issue"
msgstr "Ripoatahia mā te whakatuwhera i tētahi take GitHub hou"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:175
msgid "Please specify the language code and exact phrase when reporting."
msgstr ""
"Tēnā koa tohu te waehere reo me te rerenga kōrero tonu i te wā e tuku "
"purongo ana."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:176
msgid "Thank you for helping us make Grylli better!"
msgstr "Ngā mihi mō te āwhina i a mātou ki te whakapai ake i a Grylli!"

