msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Ngā Tohutohu Whakahaere"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:46
msgid "Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up on your host"
msgstr ""
"Whakamanahia te kōpaki raraunga (pātengi raraunga) kua pūruatia i runga i tō"
" kaihautū"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:48
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is not per user.  If required per user, you will ndd to "
"create subdirectoried per user and setup permissions so users can only see "
"their own folder."
msgstr ""
"Ehara te kōpaki tukuake i te mō ia kaiwhakamahi. Ki te hiahia mō ia "
"kaiwhakamahi, me hanga koe i ngā kōpaki iti mō ia kaiwhakamahi me te "
"whakatakoto whakaaetanga kia kite ngā kaiwhakamahi i tō rātou ake kōpaki "
"anake."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:51
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the data/grylli.db with one"
" from the backups folder, and restart the container."
msgstr ""
"Hei whakahoki mai i te pūrua: aukatia te ipu, whakakapihia te data/grylli.db"
" ki tētahi mai i te kōpaki pūrua, ka tīmata anō i te ipu."

